<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section is comprised of <ref href="/us/pl/117/167/s10361">section 10361 of Pub. L. 117–167</ref>. Subsec. (d) of <ref href="/us/pl/117/167/s10361">section 10361 of Pub. L. 117–167</ref> amended <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s1862i">section 1862i of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
